// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2572 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: cbd62511-5061-5c97-9044-30d6e5de5ed8

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
